channel.title: Runescape the 4 god war!
channel.description:
RUNESCAPE WAR SERVER IS ALMOST COMPLETE. RUNESCAPE WEBSITE FOR IT IS ALMOST COMPLETE. WHEN YOU DOWNLOAD THE SERVER YOU CANT CREATE AN ACCOUNT YET YOU HAVE TO REGISTER ON THE WEBSITE AND EITHER YOU JOIN WITH SARADOMIN,ZAMMY,GUTHIX, OR ZAROS. IF YOU DONT KNOW ZAROS GO TO WWW.ZYBEZ.NET
THE SERVER WILL NOT BE PLAYING MOPARSCAPE. IT WILL BE PLAYING FULL SCREEN. ITS NOT RUNESCAPE GRAPHICS ITS SILKROAD GRAPHICS. AND WHEN YOU LOG IN YOUR STATS WILL BE ALL 99 INCLUDING HUNTER
SILKROAD GRAPHICS TO MAKE RUNESCAPE AREAS IS : 4.3% COMPLETE WEBSITE IS : 1.2% COMPLETE NPC AND MONSTERS: 5.1%COMPLETE SARADOMIN LAND: 2.8% COMPLETE ZAMMY LAND: 2.1% COMPLETE GUTHIX LAND: 4.2% COMPLETE ZAROS LAND: 1.4% COMPLETE
SARADOMIN NPC SOLDIERS (MELEE,RANGE,MAGE) WILL BE FIRST NAME AS HOLY____ LIKE HOLY MONKS ZAMMY WILL BE UNHOLY_____ GUTHIX I DONT KNOW YET ZAROS DONT KNOW YET
FOR THE NOT PLAYING ON MOPARSCAPE I'M CREATING A LAUNCH CLIENT JUST LIKE IN SILKROADS.
THIS WILL NOT BE LIKE NORMAL RUNESCAPE. YOU WILL SEE AND CONTROL YOUR CHARACTER SMOOTHLY.
THE OBJECTIVES ARE TO KILL THE GOD WHO YOUR BATTLING WITH.
IM IN THE GUTHIX ARMY. RIGHT FLANK COMMANDER MUMAKIL.
YOU WILL EXPIERIENCE THE RIDING OF HORSES.
IN RUNESCAPE YOUR ATTACK IS ONLY LIKE 1 COMBO RIGHT? WELL THAT MAKES IT 2 WITH SPECIAL
I WILL MULTI COMBO THE RUNESCAPE ATTACKS. SO THATS WHY YOU WILL START WITH EVERY STATS 99 AND THEN WORK YOUR WAY UP TO 1000 AND YOUR COMBAT LEVEL SHOULD BE 10000. YOU SAY IM CRAZY WELL IM WORKING ON IT. THATS WHY IT WILL TAKE 2 YEARS OR MORE. AND IM LUCKY I ALREADY HAVE BOTH OF THE GAMES CODES.
THE ATTACKS IS GOING TO BE LIKE IN SILKROAD. IN RUNESCAPE YOU HAVE A SHIELD WICH YOU CANT BLOCK. IN SILKROAD YOU DO. SO IM GOING TO MAKE THAT HAPPEN. IN RUNESCAPE YOUR SPEACIAL IS LIKE 100% AND IF U USE A SPECIAL IT TAKES LIKE 25% FOR A DDS. IN SILKROAD YOU HAVE UNLIMITED MANA WICH IS YOUR SPECIAL AND IF IT RUNS OUT YOU HAVE A POTION THAT REFILLS YOUR ENERGY SO YOU CAN DO MORE SPECIAL. :| AINT IT CRAYZ!??
THE MAGES. IF YOUR IN SARADOMIN ALL YOUR NORMAL CASTS WILL BE SARADOMIN STRIKE. IN ZAROS YOU WILL USE THE WAVE SPELLS. AND YOU CAN DO ANCIENT ANYTIME YOU WANT. THE CITY TELEPORTS WILL NOT BE ACTUALY IN THE CITY. IF ITS VARROCK TELEPORT AND YOUR IN THE ZAMMORAK ARMY YOU WILL BE TELEPORTED SOMEWHERE IN THE ZAMMORAK LANDS. I WILL ADD SILKROAD MAGE SPELLS WHICH ARE, LIGHTNING, ICE, AND FIRE SPELLS SUCH AS TIGERS THUNDER BOLT, SNOW STROM ICE SHOT, FLAME WAVE BURNING. SAME AS THE RANGERS.
YOU WILL HAVE RUNESCAPE "STATS" NOT SKILLS. BUT YOU WILL HAVE SILKROAD "WEAPON SKILLS" NOT STATS.
HOW THE GAME WILL LOOK LIKE: YOU WILL MOVE YOUR CHARACTER LIKE SILKROAD. THIER WILL BE NO SILKROAD WEAPONS. ONLY RUNESCAPE WEAPONS AND ARMORS.
AND THATS IT IT'S GOING TO BE A LONG WORK. I HAVE 6 PEOPLE WORKING WITH IT.
THIS [s]SERVER[/s] [glow=red,2,300]GAME[/glow] IS GOING TO BE COMPLETED IN ABOUT 2008
